Name: House Cunningham
Description: House Cunningham is a minor noble family in the Federated Suns. his family made its fortunes centuries ago by becoming the owners of the largest agricultural producers on the planet Kestrel.
ReputationStatements: House Cunningham is glad you've answered our call. We have few other options.
